{"tid":1834031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎：病毒有變異可能 確診及死亡人數攀升","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:31:09.000Z","uid":134880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"385f4c4ea3a3bc848beb923b5a466be11fabeb3e","tid":1834031,"uid":134880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"中國官方星期三（1月22日）公布武漢肺炎最新病例數據，截至21日凌晨12點，中國新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例440例，累積死亡個案9例。<br />\n<br />\n中國專家研判認為，病例主要與武漢相關，已出現了人傳人和醫務人員感染，並存在一定範圍的社區傳播。<br />\n<br />\n病毒變異可能性<br />\n<br />\n中國國家衛生健康委員會副主任李斌在新聞發佈會上表示，新型冠狀病毒傳染源尚未找到，疫情傳播途徑尚未完全掌握，病毒存在變異的可能，疫情存在進一步擴散的風險。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51202544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-51202544&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fab5d0e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-51202544</a>"},{"pid":"26cd34cbfefa15402acade7db19a3586936b7971","tid":1834031,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"病毒存在變異的可能 = 已經變異 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}